title: Ether.One-CODEX
description:
Ether One

Release Date : 3/2014 Protection : -
Discs : 1 Genre : Action

Ether One is a first person adventure that deals with the
fragility of the human mind.

There are two paths in the world you can choose from. At
it's core is a story exploration path free from puzzles where
you can unfold the story at your own pace.

- Extract
- Burn or mount the .iso
- Run setup and install the game
- Play
